                "invention-title": [
                    "Method for realizing zero-carbon metallurgy by hydrogen-rich carbon circulating oxygen blast furnace",
                    "一种富氢碳循环氧气高炉实现零碳冶金的方法"
                ]
            },
            "abstract": [
                {
                    "p": "The invention discloses a method for realizing zero-carbon metallurgy by a hydrogen-rich carbon circulating oxygen blast furnace, which realizes carbon reduction at the input end of the hydrogen-rich carbon circulating oxygen blast furnace through extreme energy efficiency utilization of the hydrogen-rich carbon circulating oxygen blast furnace. Due to the fact that the coke further has the functions of a reducing agent, a framework and a heat generating agent in the hydrogen-rich carbon circulating oxygen blast furnace, in order to improve the liquid permeability of slag iron in the furnace, the most important function is the framework function, part of the coke still needs to be added, and after the raw materials and the solid fuel coke are added into the hydrogen-rich carbon circulating oxygen blast furnace through the furnace top crude fuel adding device, the coke is generated. And carrying out chemical reaction with oxygen blown into the hydrogen-rich carbon circulating oxygen blast furnace."
                },
                {
                    "p": "本发明公开了一种富氢碳循环氧气高炉实现零碳冶金的方法，通过富氢碳循环氧气高炉的极致能效利用实现富氢碳循环氧气高炉输入端减碳，主要包括煤气脱碳循环，由于焦炭在富氢碳循环氧气高炉内部还具有“还原剂、骨架、发热剂”的作用，其中为了炉内渣铁的透液性，最重要的是骨架作用，仍需要加入部分焦炭，炉顶原燃料加入装置将原料和固体燃料焦炭加入富氢碳循环氧气高炉后，与吹入富氢碳循环氧气高炉的氧气发生化学反应。"
                }
            ]
        }
